            <title>[CASSANDRA-6072] NPE in Pig CassandraStorage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6072</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;key_alias can be null for tables created from thrift.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Which causes an NPE here:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-1.2/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/hadoop/pig/AbstractCassandraStorage.java#L633&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-1.2/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/hadoop/pig/AbstractCassandraStorage.java#L633&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
